TW</name><order>300</order><priority>100</priority><rest_method/><rest_method_text/><rest_service/><rest_service_text/><rest_variables/><role_conditions/><script><![CDATA[(function executeRule(current, previous /*null when async*/ ) {



    var vserviceCI = current.parent.cmdb_ci;
    var vserviceCIClass = current.parent.cmdb_ci.sys_class_name;
    var vgetTechValue = '';
    var vServiceOffering = current.parent.service_offering;
	var vServiceOfferingGroup = current.parent.service_offering.u_service_group;
    var province = 'QC';

    if (current.u_province != '' && current.u_province != null && current.u_province != undefined) {
        province = current.u_province;
    } else {
        current.u_province = 'QC';
    }

    var values = [];
    var vWorkgrp = "";


    var tqServiceOffData = {

        '4469b79a476b665835f71ba4116d43e9': ['PBX', 'TC2_TC3', 'COPPER', 'CPS Voice'], //WPaaS - TELUS Cloud Collaboration (TC2) / TELUS Cloud Collaboration (TC2)
        'ee0afbda476b665835f71ba4116d434e': ['PBX', 'TC2_TC3', 'COPPER', 'CPS Voice'], //WPaaS - Service de communications unifiées / Unified Communications Service
        'c15b7bd247ab665835f71ba4116d43eb': ['VOICE', 'POTS', 'COPPER', 'Installation & Repair'], //WPaaS - Service Ligne d'affaires (1FL) / Business Line (1FL) Service
        '50b1e734476762d435f71ba4116d431b': ['WAN_L2_L3', 'WAN_L2_L3', 'WIRELESS', 'Enhanced Services'], //WPaaS - Service d'accès IP/MPLS / IP/MPLS Access Service
        'f623a7b8476762d435f71ba4116d4369': ['WAN_L2_L3', 'WAN_L2_L3_TQ', 'FIBRE', 'Enhanced Services'], //WPaaS - Service Internet Affaires N3 (SIA-N3) - TM UM CM / (SIA/BIB)CM TM UM N3 Fibre Internet Service(SIA/BIB)CM TM UM N3 Fibre Internet Service
        '35542ec247d0fa1835f71ba4116d43f5': ['NAAS', 'NAAS', 'OTT', 'Installation & Repair'], //WPaaS - Service Réseau Intelligent (NaaS) - VPN avec encryption / NaaS Service - VPN with encryption
        '096ae0362bd072d81773f7e3d891bf20': ['NAAS', 'NAAS', 'OTT', 'Installation & Repair'], //WPaaS - Service de Réseau Intelligent - Coupe-Feu Nouvelle Génération / Naas - Next Generation Firewall Service
        'a9a7f045472ba2d435f71ba4116d43f3': ['MANAGED_LAN', 'CPS_WIFI_CISCO', 'COPPER', 'CPS LAN'], //WPaaS - Service de réseau local sans-fil (WLAN) / Wireless LAN (WLAN) Service
        '2fc533ee2b9cbe981773f7e3d891bf27': ['MANAGED_LAN', 'CPS_WIFI_CISCO', 'COPPER', 'CPS LAN'], //WPaaS - Service de réseau local sans-fil (WLAN) MPaaS / Wireless LAN (WLAN) Service MPaaS
        '419a7e782b2f26101773f7e3d891bf90': ['MANAGED_LAN', 'CPS_LAN', 'COPPER', 'CPS LAN'], //WPaaS - Service de réseau local (LAN) / Local Area Network (LAN) Service
        '1473f3a22b5cbe981773f7e3d891bf9b': ['MANAGED_LAN', 'CPS_LAN', 'COPPER', 'CPS LAN'], //WPaaS - Service de réseau local (LAN) MPaaS / Local Area Network (LAN) Service MPaaS
		'06883a252b97a2941773f7e3d891bf52': ['VOICE', 'POTS_TQ', 'COPPER'],		//TQ - Ligne unique - lignes multiples / Single Line - Multi Line
        '9e773a212b97a2941773f7e3d891bf86': ['HS', 'DSL_TQ', 'GPON'],			//TQ - Fibre réseau GPON / Fiber - GPON
        'f33772ed2b57a2941773f7e3d891bf99': ['HS', 'DSL_TQ', 'COPPER'],			//TQ - ADSL / HSIA
        'a4d8d4dd4708f61035f71ba4116d43f8': ['BUS_LINE_INTERNET', 'BUS_INTERNET_TQ', 'FIBRE'],		//TQ - Accès Internet Affaires géré (Fibre) / Managed BI (Fibre)
        '04e8d8dd4708f61035f71ba4116d43db': ['BUS_LINE_INTERNET', 'BUS_INTERNET_TQ', 'COPPER'],		//TQ - Accès Internet Affaires géré (Cuivre) / Managed BI (Copper)
        'c95832652b97a2941773f7e3d891bfd4': ['VOICE', 'POTS_TQ', 'COPPER'],							//TQ - Centrex / Centrex
        '24f8d0dd4708f61035f71ba4116d43f8': ['PRIVATE_LINE', 'PRI_BRI_TQ', 'COPPER'],				//TQ - Accès primaire / PRI
        '7838f2252b97a2941773f7e3d891bfc9': ['WAN_L2_L3', 'WAN_L2_L3_TQ', 'FIBRE'],					//TQ - DID / DID
        'e7f77ea12b97a2941773f7e3d891bf65': ['WAN_L2_L3', 'WAN_L2_L3_TQ', 'FIBRE'],					//TQ - IP Trunking / IP Trunking
        'd748545d4708f61035f71ba4116d43e1': ['BUS_LINE_INTERNET', 'BUS_INTERNET_TQ', 'COPPER'],		//TQ - Accès Internet Affaires géré (ADSL VPOP) / Managed BI (ADSL VPOP)
        'dbf8d8dd4708f61035f71ba4116d43e3': ['WAN_L2_L3', 'WAN_L2_L3_TQ', 'FIBRE'],					//TQ - Utilisation de la passerelle / Gateway Usage
        '7d0990114748f61035f71ba4116d43db': ['WAN_L2_L3', 'WAN_L2_L3_TQ', 'FIBRE'],					//TQ - Accès à distance / Remote Access
        'c919dcdd4708f61035f71ba4116d431e': ['CARRIER_ETHERNET', 'CES_TQ', 'COPPER'],				//TQ - Commutateur Ethernet fournisseur / Carrier Ethernet Switch
        '46a532e92b57a2941773f7e3d891bf66': ['THIRD_WAVE', 'SDS_WIFI_TQ', 'OTT'],					//TQ - Wi-Fi TELUS Affaires / Business WIFI
        '1927b2ed2b57a2941773f7e3d891bfe8': ['CARRIER_ETHERNET', 'OPTICAL_ETHERNET_TQ', 'FIBRE'],   //TQ - ADSL (Revente Bell) / HSIA (Bell Resale)
        '2e57b6212b97a2941773f7e3d891bf8b': ['CARRIER_ETHERNET', 'OPTICAL_ETHERNET_TQ', 'FIBRE'],	//TQ - Fibre réseau GPON (Revente Bell) / Fiber - GPON (Bell Resale)
        '6da6b6ad2b57a2941773f7e3d891bf27': ['CARRIER_ETHERNET', 'OPTICAL_ETHERNET_TQ', 'FIBRE'],	//TQ - NHP / NHP
        '405998114748f61035f71ba4116d4396': ['CABLE_REPAIR', 'CABLE_REPAIR', 'COPPER'],    			//TQ - NOC / NOC
        'dac7be612b97a2941773f7e3d891bf99': ['PRIVATE_LINE', 'DS0_DS1_DS3_TQ', 'COPPER'],			//TQ - IPv4 / IPv4
        '2ea7b6612b97a2941773f7e3d891bfd9': ['PRIVATE_LINE', 'DS0_DS1_DS3_TQ', 'COPPER'],			//TQ - BVoIP / BVoIP
        '1de7fa612b97a2941773f7e3d891bfc5': ['PRIVATE_LINE', 'DS0_DS1_DS3_TQ', 'COPPER'],			//TQ - SIP Trunking / SIP Trunking
        '2739dcdd4708f61035f71ba4116d4325': ['WAN_L2_L3', 'WAN_L2_L3_TQ', 'FIBRE'],					//TQ - Fibre noire / Dark Fiber
        'efa7d231db18d09447f758b8dc96199d': ['NAAS', 'NAAS_TQ', 'OTT'],			//Network as a Service - NaaS
		'20832d1b2b77ae581773f7e3d891bf34': ['HS', 'DSL', 'COPPER'], 			// Haute vitesse/High Speed		
		'982a869f2b7fae581773f7e3d891bfb1': ['VOICE', 'POTS', 'COPPER'], 		// Téléphonie résidentielle/Home Phone 
		'6ab969132bf7ae581773f7e3d891bf95': ['VOICE', 'POTS', 'WIRELESS'], 		// VOW (Voice Over Wireless)
		'b26aed932bf7ae581773f7e3d891bfaa': ['IPTV', 'TTV', 'COPPER'], 			// Télé OPTIK (ancien)Optik TV (Legacy)
		'940da99b2bf7ae581773f7e3d891bfbc': ['SECURITY', 'SECURITY', 'OTT'] 	// Maison connectée/SmartHome Security
		
    };

    var isTqService = false;
    if (tqServiceOffData[vServiceOffering]) {
        isTqService = true;
        values = tqServiceOffData[vServiceOffering];
    }

    current.u_wfm_job_type = values[0];
    current.u_wfm_product_category = values[1];
    current.u_wfm_technology = values[2];
	if (isTqService) {
		vWorkgrp = 'NA';
	}

	var serviceOfferingsforRClass = [
		'20832d1b2b77ae581773f7e3d891bf34', 			// Haute vitesse/High Speed		
		'982a869f2b7fae581773f7e3d891bfb1', 		// Téléphonie résidentielle/Home Phone 
		'6ab969132bf7ae581773f7e3d891bf95', 		// VOW (Voice Over Wireless)
		'b26aed932bf7ae581773f7e3d891bfaa', 			// Télé OPTIK (ancien)Optik TV (Legacy)
		'940da99b2bf7ae581773f7e3d891bfbc' // Maison connectée/SmartHome Security
	];

	if (vServiceOffering && serviceOfferingsforRClass.includes(vServiceOffering.toString())) {
		current.u_wfm_service_class = 'R';
	}	

    if (values.length == 4) { // Set Project code only if passed in array.
        vWorkgrp = values[3];
    }


    var voutOfService = false;
    if (current.parent.u_condition == "Out of Service") {
        voutOfService = true;
    }


    //STRY0862761 Additional requirement  to set expected duration
    var grWfmEstDur = new GlideRecord("u_wfm_mappings");
    grWfmEstDur.addEncodedQuery("u_service_class=B^u_job_type=" + values[0] + "^u_technology=" + values[2] + "^u_product=" + values[1]);
    grWfmEstDur.query();
    if (grWfmEstDur.next()) {
        current.u_wfm_duration = grWfmEstDur.u_estimated_duration;
    }



    current.u_work_group = vWorkgrp;
	//Code for STRY0941556
    if ((current.u_province == 'QC' || current.u_province == 'Quebec'|| current.u_province == 'QUEBEC / QUÉBEC'|| current.u_province == 'QUEBEC') && vServiceOffering !='b26aed932bf7ae581773f7e3d891bfaa' &&
	vServiceOffering !='940da99b2bf7ae581773f7e3d891bfbc' &&
	vServiceOffering !='6ab969132bf7ae581773f7e3d891bf95' &&
	vServiceOffering !='982a869f2b7fae581773f7e3d891bfb1' &&
	vServiceOffering !='20832d1b2b77ae581773f7e3d891bf34' &&
	vServiceOffering !='405998114748f61035f71ba4116d4396' 
	// && vServiceOfferingGroup!='1dce6c8c2b00fe981773f7e3d891bffd'
	 ) {

    // 1. Force Workgroup to NA
    current.u_work_group = 'NA';

    // 2. Append "TQ" if not already present
    var prodCat = current.u_wfm_product_category;
    if (prodCat && !prodCat.endsWith('TQ')) {
        current.u_wfm_product_category = prodCat + '_TQ';
    }
}
    current.setWorkflow(false);
    current.update();
    current.setWorkflow(true);

})(current, previous);

function vgetTech(vCI, vServiceOffering, vserviceCIClass) {

    var vSTN = new GlideRecord(vserviceCIClass);
    if (vSTN.get(vCI)) {
        var vClass = vSTN.sys_class_name;
        var vSECode = '';
        if (vserviceCIClass == 'u_cmdb_ci_service_telephone_number') {
            vSECode = vSTN.u_nc_s_e_code.toString();
        }
        var vIndus = vSTN.company.u_industries_hospitality;

        if (vClass == "u_cmdb_ci_telus_copper" || vClass == "u_cmdb_ci_service_telephone_number" && vSECode.indexOf("BOND") == -1) {
            return "COPPER";
        }

        if (vClass == "u_cmdb_ci_service_telephone_number" && vSECode.indexOf("BOND") != -1) {
            return "COPPER_BONDED";
        }

        if (vClass == "u_cmdb_ci_telus_fiber" && vIndus.indexOf("Hospitality") != -1 && vIndus) {
            return "ETTS";
        }

        if (vClass == "u_cmdb_ci_telus_fiber") {
            return "GPON";
        }

        if (vClass == "cmdb_ci_wap_network") {
            return "WIRELESS";
        }

    }
}]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>x372111</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2025-10-28 18:43:09</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>false</sys_customer_update><sys_domain>global</sys_domain><sys_domain_path>/</sys_domain_path><sys_id>f67051762b7cfed41773f7e3d891bf73</sys_id><sys_mod_count>28</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Populate Fields based on mapping - TW</sys_name><sys_overrides/><sys_package display_value="Global" source="global">global</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_f67051762b7cfed41773f7e3d891bf73</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>x239153</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2025-11-29 07:33:39</sys_updated_on><template/><when>after</when></sys_script><sys_translated_text action="delete_multiple" query="documentkey=f67051762b7cfed41773f7e3d891bf73"/></record_update>
